title: Jimmy Fallon to be honored by Harvard Lampoon - Milwaukee Journal-Sentinal
text:
The Tonight Show host and Saturday Night Live alum is being honored Saturday by the Harvard Lampoon, the country's oldest continuously published humor magazine. The Harvard Lampoon's Facebook page says the comedian will be crowned "Emperor of Comedy" and paraded through Harvard Square in a Roman chariot.
 Milwaukee Journal-Sentinal.
